<p>
<note n="0671005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0671005">勝＝益【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0672002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0672002">（四）＋食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
